    </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This spell is a lightning based Area Effect. Does 16-25 (max) damage to Target.
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
