			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Invoke Lightning is a AoE spell with a very small radius (so small that the mobs have to almost be in exactly the same place).  With regards as to whether or not it will harm group member and their pets is as follows:<BR>
<BR>
If you play on a PvP server, the spell will effect your group members and pets.<BR>
<BR>
If you are on a non-PvP server, the spell will not harm group members or their pets, but will still harm you if cast on yourself or if you are in the AoE range.
				</font>
			</td>

