	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Here's my experience when using this spell in Crushbone:<BR>
<BR>
I was grouped when the puller pulled Emperor, Prophet, emmisary, royal guard, and a legionaire. This wasn't too promising :)<BR>
<BR>
I used this spell every chance I got, saving just enough mana for snares. Needless to say, we dealt a lot of damage before having to run (in which case I snared a few orcs, rooted a few more, and we all ran). So, this spell is not good when used against one enemy. Neither is it very good when soloing. It is usually a spell that is casted when you are grouped, and the puller didn't know what he was doing.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
